{"tid":837880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：我絕對不會就此退休","createTime":"2018-09-26T16:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T04:39:18.000Z","uid":46892,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07e436ee1221260f936c3b406546b8c75a5f3e8e","tid":837880,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"據《倫敦晚旗報》消息，前阿仙奴教練雲格否認了自己即將退休的消息，但他尚未確定何時會再次重新執教。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格目前還不急於決定未來的去向，他近日出席了國際足協的年度最佳頒獎典禮。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格說：「說實話，我現在真的沒有考慮過未來的事情，因為我當時就確定在離開阿仙奴之後的幾個月之內，不會做出任何決定。所以我對此並不擔心，我還沒考慮過這個問題。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「但我肯定不會選擇退休，如果我真的打算退休，我可能在很就之前就會這麼做了。下個月我就69歲了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　在被問到他是否會執教其他球隊時，雲格說：「我不知道，目前我真的不知道。」"},{"pid":"1585ee0d689384312508b1072974e8c459d86973","tid":837880,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"雲膠強勢回歸！"},{"pid":"5827cbd02e5b5398017425f5c55b31fb6beaa181","tid":837880,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"同山神團聚"},{"pid":"0a0c8169070d1ae458c50601f6689c5770554127","tid":837880,"uid":13391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"爺爺出山拯救魚拉突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dba2bb8a4729446d42fb4a81f1099c4f4e5f4b","tid":837880,"uid":35930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"好似以前賣球員去死敵，今次自己加盟死敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n魚拉突 啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c688ab3eb692c0b42222943ac3a3e0fcffd3f697","tid":837880,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"係咪暗示愛蛇遲早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censor